00:59:59,530 --> 01:00:02,680
the engine sputtered to a halt.

583
01:00:02,680 --> 01:00:07,980
He stepped off the porch and began to approach
her, walking easily, then suddenly stopped

584
01:00:07,980 --> 01:00:15,770
cold as she emerged from the car. For a long
