01:01:25,170 --> 01:01:29,780
Thoughts of the summer they’d shared came
back to her, and as she stared at him, she

597
01:01:29,780 --> 01:01:37,369
noticed how little he’d changed since she’d
last seen him. He looked good, she thought.

598
01:01:37,369 --> 01:01:43,050
With his shirt tucked loosely into old faded
jeans, she could see the same broad shoulders

599
01:01:43,050 --> 01:01:49,850
she remembered, tapering down to narrow hips
