01:01:59,930 --> 01:02:05,529
When she was finally ready, she took a deep
breath and smiled.

603
01:02:05,529 --> 01:02:11,079
“Hello, Noah. It’s good to see you again.”

604
01:02:11,079 --> 01:02:17,279
Her comment startled him, and he looked at
her with amazement in his eyes. Then, after

