01:06:09,990 --> 01:06:16,890
She turned away and took a deep breath, wondering
how to say it, and when she finally started,

647
01:06:16,890 --> 01:06:23,310
her voice was quiet. “Noah, before you get
the wrong idea, I did want to see you again,

