01:07:11,549 --> 01:07:17,859
Noah nodded, feeling the tightness in his
stomach. “Actually it’s a she. Clementine’s

661
01:07:17,859 --> 01:07:24,810
her name. But yeah, she’s all mine.” They
both watched as Clem shook her head, stretched,

662
01:07:24,810 --> 01:07:30,760
then wandered toward the sounds. Allie’s
eyes widened just a bit when she saw her limp

663
01:07:30,760 --> 01:07:31,760
away.

