753
01:14:17,080 --> 01:14:22,199
“Yes,” he answered, volunteering no more.

754
01:14:22,199 --> 01:14:24,960
“Do you ever think about it?”

755
01:14:24,960 --> 01:14:31,510
“Sometimes,” he said. “Usually when
