765
01:15:22,429 --> 01:15:25,860
the only time.”

766
01:15:25,860 --> 01:15:30,830
Her comment made both of them drift back and
remember as they slowly circled back to the

767
01:15:30,830 --> 01:15:37,449
house, following a new path that passed near
