771
01:15:46,639 --> 01:15:50,630
“Is your fiancé here on business?”

772
01:15:50,630 --> 01:15:59,199
She shook her head. “No, he’s still in
Raleigh.” Noah raised his eyebrows. “Does

773
01:15:59,199 --> 01:16:02,120
he know you’re here?”

774
01:16:02,120 --> 01:16:10,889
She shook her head again and answered slowly.
“No. I told him I was looking for antiques.

775
01:16:10,889 --> 01:16:15,290
He wouldn’t understand my coming here.”

776
01:16:15,290 --> 01:16:21,280
Noah was a little surprised by her answer.
