1213
01:53:08,119 --> 01:53:11,810
“You’re right. I just miss him, is all.”

1214
01:53:11,810 --> 01:53:14,290
“I liked him, too. He made me laugh.”

1215
01:53:14,290 --> 01:53:17,650
