1244
01:55:51,030 --> 01:55:56,099
wondered what she’d thought about his life,
hoping it would somehow make a difference,

1245
01:55:56,099 --> 01:55:59,199
if it could.

1246
01:55:59,199 --> 01:56:03,770
Noah got up and refilled the teapot. They
both brought the dishes to the sink and cleaned

1247
01:56:03,770 --> 01:56:08,989
up the table, and he poured two more cups
