1297
02:01:16,159 --> 02:01:19,719
simple as not being second.

1298
02:01:19,719 --> 02:01:28,429
Noah, too, was sifting through his thoughts.
To him, the evening would be remembered as

1299
02:01:28,429 --> 02:01:35,230
one of the most special times he had ever
