1346
02:05:55,739 --> 02:05:59,159
“I’d like that.”

1347
02:05:59,159 --> 02:06:04,909
Noah was surprised. He hadn’t expected her
to answer this way. He wanted to touch her

1348
02:06:04,909 --> 02:06:07,699
