1363
02:06:58,980 --> 02:07:05,139
“See you tomorrow,” she said, her eyes
reflecting the moonlight.

1364
02:07:05,139 --> 02:07:09,929
Noah waved as she backed the car out. She
turned it around, then drove up the lane,

1365
02:07:09,929 --> 02:07:16,360
heading toward town. He watched the car until
the lights vanished behind far-off oak trees

1366
02:07:16,360 --> 02:07:23,020
