1367
02:07:23,020 --> 02:07:28,940
paying special attention to her neck, scratching
the spot she couldn’t reach anymore. After

1368
02:07:28,940 --> 02:07:35,830
he looked up the road one last time, they
returned to the back porch side by side.

1369
02:07:35,830 --> 02:07:41,239
He sat in the rocker again, this time alone,
trying once again to fathom the evening that

1370
02:07:41,239 --> 02:07:48,679
had just passed. Thinking about it. Replaying
it. Seeing it again. Hearing it again. Running

1371
02:07:48,679 --> 02:07:54,829
it by in slow motion. He didn’t feel like
