1408
02:11:09,780 --> 02:11:12,110
His mind clicked.

1409
02:11:12,110 --> 02:11:18,940
Something . . . something . . . something
said? Something had been said? Yes, that was

1410
02:11:18,940 --> 02:11:24,520
