3538
05:31:31,200 --> 05:31:39,050
I finally exit my room anyway, slow-shuffle,
slide-the-right, slow-shuffle. It takes aeons

3539
05:31:39,050 --> 05:31:45,860
to close the distance, but for some reason
she does not see me approaching. I am a silent

3540
05:31:45,860 --> 05:31:52,930
panther creeping through the jungle, I am
