3550
05:32:24,610 --> 05:32:25,910
“I remember.”

3551
05:32:25,910 --> 05:32:28,440
“Then you know you shouldn’t be doing
this.”

3552
05:32:28,440 --> 05:32:35,790
I don’t answer directly. Instead I say,
“I miss her.” “I know you do, but I

3553
05:32:35,790 --> 05:32:37,240
can’t let you see her.”

3554
05:32:37,240 --> 05:32:44,150
“It’s our anniversary,” I say. This
