3555
05:32:44,150 --> 05:32:45,600
years today.

3556
05:32:45,600 --> 05:32:47,202
“I see.”

3557
05:32:47,202 --> 05:32:50,320
“Then I can go?”

3558
05:32:50,320 --> 05:32:55,138
